  "text": "A cell contains nuclei and cytoplasmic organelles, and a brain tissue consists of cortex, white matter, and basal ganglia. Indeed, a previous study showed that porcine white matter contained more lipid than gray matter [CITATION_1] . In this study, we standardized the heterogeneity by collecting spectra from adequate amount of spots distributed on the entire surface.",
